"Jockstrap 的泰勒·斯凯和乔治亚·埃勒里。信用。埃迪·惠兰 (1)" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Taylor-Skye-and-Georgia-Ellery-of-Jockstrap.-Credit.-Eddie-Whelan-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a>宣布推出“I&lt;3UQTINVU”，这是他们首张专辑的混音版本，由 Taylor Skye 制作。<b></b></p><ul><li aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709">Jockstrap – “I Love You Jennifer B”评论：神奇、迷人的首次亮相 – 也是年度最佳之一</a></b></li></ul><p>《I&lt;3UQTINVU》是《I Love You Cutie, I Envy You》的缩写，是对 Jockstrap 2022 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《I Love You Jennifer B》</a>的更新。混音版由 Skye 策划，她与 Georgia Ellery 一起组成了 Jockstrap 二人组之一。</p><p> Skye 为《I Love You Jennifer B》中的每首歌制作了混音版，以在专辑创作过程中保持灵感。斯凯在一份新闻声明中说：“其中一些混音版已经有近三年的历史了，有些只有六个月的历史。” “在混音专辑时这样做让我保持理智。”</p><p>定于 11 月 3 日发行的《I&lt;3UQTINVU》已与 IAN STARR 合作的主打单曲《Red Eye》进行了预览。新单曲附有由 Liam Noonan 拍摄的音乐视频，其中 STARR、Ellery 和 Skye 在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/boygenius-fred-again-primal-scream-to-headline-scotlands-connect-festival-2023-3407807" target="_blank" rel="noopener">今年的 Connect Festival</a>上表演。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Jockstrap 和 Taylor Skye - Red Eye ft. Ian Starr" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MNMIFU1zogY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我喜欢创作能够突破我的声音和能量极限的歌曲，”斯塔尔说。 “我竭尽全力在《红眼》中打造出最疯狂的表演。” STARR 与其他特色艺术家 Ersatz、Coby Sey 等一起出现在《I&lt;3UQTINVU》中。</p><p>上个月，Jockstrap 凭借《I Love You Jennifer B》的作品入围 2023 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/mercury-prize">水星奖</a>入围名单，其他提名者包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arctic-monkeys">Arctic Monkeys</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/arctic-monkeys-the-car-review-3330197">《The Car》</a> ）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">Loyle Carner</a> （ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/loyle-carner-hugo-review-an-honest-unflashy-storyteller-3332632">《Hugo》</a> ）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Olivia Dean</a> （《I Love You Jennifer B <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-dean-messy-review-debut-album-radar-3463419" target="_blank" rel="noopener">》）</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/olivia-dean-messy-review-debut-album-radar-3463419" target="_blank" rel="noopener">凌乱&#39;</a> ）等。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective</a>最终凭借他们的第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-new-album-where-im-meant-to-be-sampa-the-great-life-goes-on-3296522" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《Where I&#39;m Meant To Be》</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ezra-collective-win-the-2023-mercury-prize-for-where-im-meant-to-be-3494841">获得了水星奖</a>。</p><p> “过去一年的反响非常好，”本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jockstrap-tease-new-collaborative-single-and-share-love-of-irish-folk-band-lankum-3495281">埃勒里在水星奖红地毯上告诉<em>《NME》</em></a> 。 “我们非常幸运。有一些伟大的节日，人们一起唱歌。无法要求更多。”</p><p> 《I Love You Jennifer B》去年 9 月发行后获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jockstrap-i-love-you-jennifer-b-review-radar-3305709" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NME</em>的五星级评价</a>。 <i>NME</i>写道：“这对伦敦二人组对创新的不懈承诺将令新人和狂热粉丝兴奋不已。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jockstrap-remixed-version-i-love-you-jennifer-b-taylor-skye-3497001">Jockstrap 宣布泰勒·斯凯 (Taylor Skye) 获得 Mercury 提名的《I Love You Jennifer B》的混音版本</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《A Time Called You》导演透露 Rowoon 没有因为出演而获得“任何金钱” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/a-time- Called-you-director-rowoon-wasnt-paid-appearing-in-k-drama-3496972?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=a-time-打电话给你的导演路云在韩剧中出演没有报酬Puah ZiweiWed, 13 Sep 2023 03:53:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3496972 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="rowoon sf9 一次叫你" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>金振元还谈到了SF9成员是如何扮演这个角色的</p><p>《A Time Called You》的导演透露，Rowoon 在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/a-time-called-you-director-rowoon-wasnt-paid-appearing-in-k-drama-3496972">亮相并没有获得“任何报酬”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="rowoon sf9 一次叫你" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/rowoon-a-time-called-you-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>韩国歌手兼演员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rowoon">Rowoon</a>是男孩乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sf9">SF9</a>的成员，他在 Netflix 的新韩剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/a-time-called-you"><em>《A Time Called You</em></a> 》中的角色没有获得“任何报酬”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/a-time-called-you-review-netflix-k-drama-3496021">《A Time Called You》评论：身体交换、时间疯狂的浪漫</a></strong></li></ul><p>上周，Netflix 发布了最新的韩国剧集<em>《呼叫你的时光》</em> 。这部新韩剧由安孝燮（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/business-proposal"><em>《商业提案</em></a>》）和全汝彬（<em>文森佐</em>）主演，翻拍自 2019 年台湾电视剧<em>《有一天或有一天》</em> 。</p><p>该剧由路云特别出演，他饰演男主角始宪（安饰）的朋友泰河。在<a href="https://m.joynews24.com/v/1631572" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Joy24 News</em></a>的新采访中，系列导演 Kim Jin-won 透露了 Rowoon 是如何出演这个角色的，以及为什么他没有为自己的出场付费。</p><p>金说，他首先要寻找“合适的人”，因为必须是安感到“舒服”并且能产生“良好化学反应”的人。 “我问 Ahn，‘你和这个行业的任何人都是好朋友吗’，这就是我们开始讨论 Rowoon 的方式，”他补充道（由<a href="https://www.koreaboo.com/news/sf9-rowoon-cameo-friend-ahn-hyo-seop-time-called-no-payment/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Koreanaboo</em></a>翻译）。</p><p> “我与 Rowoon 的管理层取得了联系。我还请 Ahn 与 Rowoon 讨论这个角色，这样 Rowoon 就会对场景的细节有所了解，”Kim 补充道。 “经过一番讨论，Rowoon 很高兴地接受了这个提议。”</p><p> Kim 随后透露，Rowoon 并没有“为出场收取任何费用”，而只是要求以他的名义向 Ahn 发送一辆餐车。该导演还向<em>Joy24 News</em>表示，他“特别喜欢公开这一点”。</p><p>与此同时， <em>《一次叫你》的</em>女主角<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/jeon-yeo-been-pressure-remake-someday-or-one-day-a-time-called-you-3496583">全汝彬 (Jeon Yeo-been) 最近公开了她在这部新韩剧中感受到的“压力”</a> ，并表示她对台湾原版的“喜爱”。</p><p> 《A Time Called You》的导演透露，Rowoon 在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/a-time-called-you-director-rowoon-wasnt-paid-appearing-in-k-drama-3496972">亮相并没有获得“任何报酬”</a> 。</p> ;
